<div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-12">
  <h2>Purpose</h2>
  <p class="lead">
    <code>ember-sortable-table</code>is an addon component for Ember CLI applications that will give you a simple way to make your tables sortable by clicking on the table's headers. Using <a href="http://tablesorter.com" target="_blank">TableSorter by Christian Bach</a> you simply replace your standard <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> with the <code>\{{ember-sortable-table}}</code> helper. 
  </p>

